{"word":"G3718 - ὀρθοτομέω - orthotoméō - or-thot-om-eh'-o - Rightly divide","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὀρθοτομέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>orthotoméō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>or-thot-om-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Rightly divide"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிதானமாய்ப்பகு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to cut straight"},{"paragraph":"2. dropping the idea of cutting, to make straight and smooth"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a compound of <a href=\"#/G3717 - ὀρθός - orthós - or-thos'/3717\">G3717</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5114 - τομώτερος - tomṓteros - tom-o'-ter-os/5114\">G5114</a>; to <i>make</i> a <i>straight cut</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>dissect</i> (<i>expound</i>) <i>correctly</i> (the divine message): - rightly divide."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1357 - διόρθωσις - diórthōsis - dee-or'-tho-sis/1357\">G1357</a>, <a href=\"#/G1882 - ἐπανόρθωσις - epanórthōsis - ep-an-or'-tho-sis/1882\">G1882</a>, <a href=\"#/G2699 - κατατομή - katatomḗ - kat-at-om-ay'/2699\">G2699</a>, <a href=\"#/G3716 - ὀρθοποδέω - orthopodéō - or-thop-od-eh'-o/3716\">G3716</a>, <a href=\"#/G3717 - ὀρθός - orthós - or-thos'/3717\">G3717</a>, <a href=\"#/G3718 - ὀρθοτομέω - orthotoméō - or-thot-om-eh'-o/3718\">G3718</a>, <a href=\"#/G3719 - ὀρθρίζω - orthrízō - or-thrid'-zo/3719\">G3719</a>, <a href=\"#/G3720 - ὀρθρινός - orthrinós - or-thrin-os'/3720\">G3720</a>, <a href=\"#/G3721 - ὄρθριος - órthrios - or'-three-os/3721\">G3721</a>, <a href=\"#/G3722 - ὄρθρος - órthros - or'-thros/3722\">G3722</a>, <a href=\"#/G3723 - ὀρθῶς - orthōs - or-thoce'/3723\">G3723</a>, <a href=\"#/G663 - ἀποτομία - apotomía - ap-ot-om-ee'-ah/663\">G663</a>, <a href=\"#/G664 - ἀποτόμως - apotómōs - ap-ot-om'-oce/664\">G664</a>"}]}